<chapter id=Concepts>Session Manager Concepts

<procedure>Subtopics
<list plain tight>
* <xref HowSessionMgrWorksSI>
* <xref RestoringRemoteProcessesSI> 
* <xref DisplayIndependence>
<\list>

Generally, Session Manager works with little intervention
from the user. 

However, you may want to know more about how Session Manager
works if you are customizing Session Manager or
distributing session files to other systems on the network.


